title: [Ta'Vaalor, Caernaeas Var]
description: A small stand of trees crowds up against the high city wall, so thickly gathered that the wall itself is barely visible through the leafy boughs.  A small gate, closed and locked, blocks progress down the lone path that disappears into the deep green bower.

A small stand of trees crowds up against the high city wall, so thickly gathered that the wall itself is barely visible through the leafy boughs.  A rusty iron gate blocks progress down the lone path that disappears into the deep green bower.
